PrecisTransfer to the Province of British Columbia (Ministry of Forests), for a term of up to fifteen years, of the administration and control over a piece of land situate at Williams Lake Airport, together with Building No. 9, which are to be used as a base for aerial forest fire protection activities and matters and things directly related or incidental thereto.
